## 2026-03-28 - No $extends token inheritance
- Implemented DTCG `$extends` token inheritance for composite tokens (typography, shadow, border, transition, composition). Tokens can now reference a base token via `$extensions.tokenmanager.extends` and override only specific properties, inheriting the rest.
- **Core resolver** (`packages/core/src/resolver.ts`): Added `getExtendsPath()` static method, `collectAllDependencies()` to include extends targets in the dependency graph, and value merging logic in `dfsResolve()` that shallow-merges base token value with local overrides. Type resolution also inherits from the base token. Cycle detection works automatically through the existing DFS.
- **Core constants** (`packages/core/src/constants.ts` ~L42): Added `COMPOSITE_TOKEN_TYPES` set exported from `index.ts`.

